                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">The Belt of Russ has the same effect as an iron halo.
A model equipped with the Belt of Russ gets a 4+ Invulnerable Save that may be used instead of the model&apos;s Armour Save.</characteristic>
