      <infoLinks>
        <infoLink name="True Grit" id="4155-0b91-6df6-ea53" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="e516-c268-82d7-433d"/>
      </infoLinks>
      <modifiers>
        <modifier type="add" value="All Wolf Guard in an army count as a single Elites choice. You can never have more than 20 Wolf Guard in an army. A Wolf Guard Battle Leader does not count towards this limit.
All Wolf Guard (except with Mark of the Wulfen) must either be attached to a Space Wolves pack as a leader or to a Space Wolves character as a bodyguard.
For the best user experience Leaders and Bodyguards should be formed in their respective units they will be attached to, but the builders will be maintained here for use if desired. If you wish to use a Wolf Guard with the Mark of the Wulfen, they must be added to this entry.

A pack of Blood Claws or Wolf Scouts may not be led by a Wolf Guard in Terminator armour." field="info"/>
      </modifiers>
    </selectionEntry>
