        <rule name="Fire Control" id="6254-1320-2f7f-aa4a" hidden="false">
          <description>As long as the Pack Leader is still alive and doesn&apos;t shoot in the Shooting phase, then the pack may engage up to two different target units instead of one. Declare which models will fire at each target and carry on using normal rules.</description>
